The coordinate system for the local tensors is defined in Fig. 1. The zz-component is aligned with the C–2H bond direction, and the yy-component is perpendicular to any π system. For an aromatic C–2H (sp2) bond an asymmetry parameter of \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
